		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et vitae innocentiam a domino.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quia hic tabellio<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Unbekannt.</note> Cambidonam erat profecturus, volui his te salutare, amice et frater in domino venerabilis et charissime, simulque indicare, pares interea, dum ille it ac redit, ut redeu[nti a]liquid des tuarum.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego nunc quod<pb type="edition" next="272"/> scribe[rem amp]lius non habui.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepisti haud dubie, quod [nuper mi]si senatus consultum aut plebiscitum reipublicae [nostrae contra] militiam mercenariam<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Vgl. oben <ref target="file11743">Nr. 1698</ref>, 24f mit Anm. 10.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reddidit spiritum rede[mptori] Christo peste<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>Von</hi> peste <hi>bis</hi> extinctus <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> intra triduum extinctus vir doctissimus et piissimus d. <persName ref="person124">Petrus Cholinus</persName> [die 2.] decembris<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="person124">Peter Kolin</persName> starb am 2. Dezember.</note>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eadem die absoluti sunt et libri ecclesiastici sive apocryphi, quos ille multa diligentia e Graeco in Latinum transtulit, Froschouerus excudit<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Auch gemäß Bullingers Vorrede (HBBibl I 115) wurde der Druck von <persName ref="person124">Kolins</persName> Beitrag zur Anfang 1543 erschienenen "Biblia sacrosancta" (BZD C 319) an dessen Todestag fertiggestellt; s. aaO, f. a6r.</note> adiuncturus illos bibliis illis suis ad vernas nundinas evulgandis.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vetus testamentum ex Hebraeo vertit <persName ref="person114">Leo</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="person114">Leo Jud</persName>.</note> et partem d. T[heodorus] <persName ref="person14">Bibliander</persName>; in novo recognoscendo et adornando laborant atque laborarunt nostrum aliquot,<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">An der Textrevision des Neuen Testamentes war neben Kolin auch <persName ref="person84">Gwalther</persName> beteiligt; vgl. Willy <hi>Brändly,</hi> <persName ref="person124">Peter Kolin</persName> von Zug, in: Zwa 1X/3, 1950, S. 169.</note> quemadmodum videbis post mensem unum atque alterum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Elegantius<note xml:id="fnc" type="footnote" n="c"><hi>Von</hi> Elegantius <hi>bis</hi> typographus <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note> opus et pulchrius non vidit, opinor, vel Germania vel Gallia, nec ullis sumptibus parcit typographus<note xml:id="fnd" type="footnote" n="d"><hi>Von</hi> Elegantius <hi>bis</hi> typographus <hi>am Rande nachgetragen.</hi></note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus tecum.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">12. decembris anno 1542.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis tuam familiam ac fratres.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te <persName ref="person145">Megander</persName>, <persName ref="person165">Pellicanus</persName>, <persName ref="person14">Bibliander</persName> ac reliqui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus H. Bullingerus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="person19">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName>, fratri et amico syncerissimo longeque charissimo suo.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="place565">Costantz</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
